    tmp = v2

    v1 = wp.exp((wp.sin(v2 + 0.53) - (v1 + 0.62 - v2 + 0.86)))
    v2 = ((v0 + wp.abs(v1 + 0.09)) - wp.abs((v0 + 0.84 / v0 + 0.79)))
